---
title: Parma Ham Pasta in Creamy Garlic Sauce with Tenderstem® Broccoli and Ciabatta
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Parma Ham Pasta in Creamy Garlic Sauce in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R05_W48_UK_QV17193-2_Main__9low-b62b07f3.jpg
